description:
Dave Rubin tells Clay and Buck he sees the massive red pilling of America. White House: Vaxxing kids will lower inflation. Yeah, that makes complete sense, Buck sarcastically jabs. Our man in Kenosha: Julio Rosas on the Rittenhouse trial. We told you so, Clay laughs: Fauci orders boosters for all.
